news_header: Ukraine faces confusion and fear as US-Russia relations strain amid ongoing war and diplomatic tensions.
news_original_title: Ykkösaamun vieras on sotatieteiden dosentti Ilmari Käihkö – mitä haluat kysyä häneltä?
news_text: In Ukraine, confusion and fear arise over US-Russia relations. Trump blames Ukraine for the war, while Zelensky defends against accusations. Diplomatic tensions escalate as Europe reacts.
